Richard Wake-Walker - non-executive Director
Richard spent over twenty years in diamond buying and sales with De Beers, his career with them culminating in General Director of the De Beers Moscow office.  As a co-founder of WWW International Diamond Consultants Ltd, he has participated in diamonds sales and valuations worldwide since 1996 and has acted as an adviser on diamonds to several organisations and companies.  His experience and range of contacts, coupled with his knowledge of trends in the diamond market will assist Savannah in its strategy-setting and decision-making. [Link- http://www.diamondwww.com/ & http://www.polisheddiamonds.com/] 
